game.name: Annie Halloween Party
game.description:
In this one of the best fashion games for girls, you will again get a chance to enjoy the spirit of your favorite Halloween season. We are pretty sure that you would fall in love with this brand new girls game and will definitely recommend your friends and families to try it out during their free hours. So, what are you waiting for? Join Annie Halloween Party and be prepared to attend the best scary party you have witnessed during this spookiest time of the year!

Your favorite princess Anna has already invited you to join her to improve the feelings of her celebration. Enjoy the freedom of choosing anything for her, be it a vampire look, a witch style or even a pumpkin in this cool HTML5 dressing game! Everyone is waiting for her to appear in the party. Help the lady to pick up the winning costume and enjoy her favorite occasion perfectly! Check out all the spooky dresses and accessories and choose a nice scary make-up look to give her a total transformation in this princess make-up game!

Give her a chocolate, white and dark cream short dress, a shining green gown with some silver work on its bra, a white crop top combined with a colorful bottom, a black short dress, or a pink, black and green color outfit! Then help her choose a funny and spooky face makeup, hairstyle, a headband, and a matching pumpkin. When you are done, click the right-click button or you can also capture it in your camera for the future.
